  "detailed_description": "Compete against your friends in the traditional sport of petanque to determine who is the master of petanque.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The Petanque</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2075480/extras/adefb88b8876f96534e2eaf3b28f9c67.poster.avif?t=1761222887\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2075480/extras/adefb88b8876f96534e2eaf3b28f9c67.webm?t=1761222887\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2075480/extras/adefb88b8876f96534e2eaf3b28f9c67.mp4?t=1761222887\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>A simple and intuitive game, throw your ball to be closest to the cochonnet(the little golden pig). The furthest players take damage until they are eliminated.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A Revisiting of The Petanque</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2075480/extras/090630f2483baa718567c9770734ff68.poster.avif?t=1761222887\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2075480/extras/090630f2483baa718567c9770734ff68.webm?t=1761222887\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2075480/extras/090630f2483baa718567c9770734ff68.mp4?t=1761222887\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Use various magical powers to gain an advantage over your opponents and turn the tide of the game. The last one standing wins!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Everyone For Himself Or As A Team</h2>Compete against your friends alone or in a team.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Customize yourself</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2075480/extras/67e01a3a01d496048bb337379af35cbd.poster.avif?t=1761222887\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2075480/extras/67e01a3a01d496048bb337379af35cbd.webm?t=1761222887\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2075480/extras/67e01a3a01d496048bb337379af35cbd.mp4?t=1761222887\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Change your colors and outfits to differentiate yourself from others !",
